'''建造工程師'''（{{lang-en|Building engineer}}），又稱為'''建築工程師'''（{{lang-en|Architectural engineer}}），是[[建成環境|建成環境]][[科技|科技]]中的[[設計|設計]]、[[建築施工|建築施工]]、檢查及維修的專業人士<ref>{{Cite web|title=What is a Building Engineer?|url=https://cbuilde.com/page/what_is_a_building_engineer|accessdate=2021-03-30|work=Chartered Association of Building Engineers|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024055142/https://cbuilde.com/page/what_is_a_building_engineer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。建造工程師亦研究降低建築法[[能源|能源]]消耗，改善[[氣候變化|氣候變化]]及人類生活<ref>{{Cite web |title=Building Engineering (BEng) |url=https://www.concordia.ca/content/concordia/en/academics/undergraduate/building-engineering.html |accessdate=2021-03-30 |author=Gina Cody School of Engineering and Computer Science |work=Concordia University |language=en}}</ref>。

== 各地專業 ==
=== 香港 ===
香港的建造工程師可在通過考核後成為[[香港工程師學會|香港工程師學會]]建造界別（Building Discipline）會員<ref>{{Cite web |title=Discipline |url=https://www.hkie.org.hk/en/quali/discipline/ |accessdate=2021-03-30 |work=The Hong Kong Institute of Engineers |language=en |archive-date=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701105645/http://www.hkie.org.hk/en/quali/discipline/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=建造工程師簡介 |url=http://bd.hkie.org.hk/Home.aspx?SubMenuID=b843ab6e-ca7c-4edc-ab16-2ed3f0bdd98a |accessdate=2021-04-05 |work=Building Division, The Hong Kong Institution of Engineers |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117090724/http://bd.hkie.org.hk/Home.aspx?SubMenuID=b843ab6e-ca7c-4edc-ab16-2ed3f0bdd98a |dead-url=no }}</ref>。執業方面，合資格的建造工程師可以在成為香港工程師學會正式會員後，或獲[[工程師註冊管理局|工程師註冊管理局]]承認的專業資格後向局方申請成為香港註冊專業工程師（建造）<ref>{{Cite web |title=Notes to Applicants |url=https://www.erb.org.hk/notestoapplicants.htm |accessdate=2021-03-30 |work=Engineers Registration Board |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301101003/http://www.erb.org.hk/notestoapplicants.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

此外，註冊專業工程師（建造）在過去3年內獲得最少1年在香港取得興建、修葺及保養建築物的實際經驗<ref>{{Cite web |title=建築專業人士 - 屋宇署 |url=https://www.bd.gov.hk/tc/resources/registration-guides/index_building_professionals.html |accessdate=2021-03-31 |work=屋宇署 |archive-date=2019-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019201232/https://www.bd.gov.hk/tc/resources/registration-guides/index_building_professionals.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，便可在通過考核後向[[屋宇署|屋宇署]]申請成為香港法例第123章《建築物條例》下列明的註冊檢驗人員<ref>{{Cite web |title=第123章 《建築物條例》 |url=https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/checkconfig/checkClientConfig.jsp?applicationId=RA001 |accessdate=2021-03-31 |work=電子版香港法例 |archive-date=2016-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160522091502/http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/e1bf50c09a33d3dc482564840019d2f4/4ed2ff0cf02f2fd9c82564760077af3c?OpenDocument |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 英國 ===
英國[[特許建造工程師協會|特許建造工程師協會]]負責規管建造工程師專業事務，合資格人士可使用特許建造工程師（Chartered Building Engineer）銜頭<ref>{{Cite web |title=MCABE Chartered Building Engineer |url=https://cbuilde.com/page/member_chartered_building_engineer |accessdate=2021-03-31 |work=Chartered Association of Building Engineers |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024064737/https://cbuilde.com/page/member_chartered_building_engineer |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 美國 ===
美國將建造工程師稱為建築工程師（Architectural engineer）。美國工程與測量考試委員會（National Council of Examiners for Engineering and Surveying）負責制定建築工程專業考試細則，並由全美各州的工程管理當局舉行考試與註冊<ref>{{Cite web|title=NCEES PE Architectural Engineering exam information|url=https://ncees.org/engineering/pe/architectural/|accessdate=2021-03-31|work=NCEES|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424180027/https://ncees.org/engineering/pe/architectural/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外美國{{Link-en|建築工程學會|Architectural Engineering Institute}}負責促進該國業內的專業發展<ref>{{Cite web |title=Architectural Engineering Institute {{!}} ASCE |url=https://www.asce.org/architectural-engineering/architectural-engineering-institute/ |accessdate=2021-03-31 |work=American Society of Civil Engineers |language=en |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608223854/https://www.asce.org/architectural-engineering/architectural-engineering-institute/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

